Download NodeJS:
	1. Go to url -> https://nodejs.org/en/download/
	2. Depending upon operating System -> select operating system
	3. Click the downloaded executable
	4. Complete the installation process
	5. Open terminal
	6. Verify node and npm is installed.
		node -v
		npm -v


Creating new repo for Wdio-Module(node-project)
1. Create a new repo in github
2. Clone the new repo in local
3. Go in to the new repo in local
4. Create new branch
5. Checkout on the new-branch
6. Create node project
    Command: npm init â€“y
7. Install WebDriver-IO cli
    Command: npm install @wdio/cli
8. Set up wdio config file
    Command: npx wdio config
